{"id":14618,"date":"2024-02-15T17:46:39","date_gmt":"2020-09-15T12:16:39","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=14618"},"modified":"2023-10-13T12:14:28","modified_gmt":"2023-10-13T06:44:28","slug":"types-of-small-kitchen-designs","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/types-of-small-kitchen-designs\/","title":{"rendered":"Types Of Small Kitchen Designs For A Small House"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>Have a space constraint at home but don&#8217;t want to compromise on the looks of your kitchen? Then take a quick read through our latest blog on simple kitchen designs for small houses.<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>There are a set of specific rules we follow in the kitchen, whether it be a small kitchen or a big kitchen. Let&#8217;s run through the rules together shall we?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>&nbsp;If you empty it- Fill it&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you dirty it-Clean it&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you open it-Close it<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you spill it-Wipe it&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you cook it &#8211; Share it!&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Aren&#8217;t these rules simple? Well, you all know that rules must be followed to keep your kitchen tidy. If you have a small home and are looking for small kitchen ideas, then this is the blog for you.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Simple Kitchen Design For Small House With Vertical Garden Concept<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you believe in simplicity then this simple kitchen design for your small house is just right. This kitchen has overhead cabinets with a lift-up mechanism and bottom cabinets with drawers designed with handles. The backsplash in this kitchen is made from mosaic tiles and has LED strip lighting. A vertical garden concept has been integrated into this simple kitchen design which peps up the place in a simplistic way. This kitchen has a seamless black granite slab that is sleek in its design. Room for wicker baskets is provided to store fruit and vegetables.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/15172302\/simple-kitchen-design-for-small-house-with-certicle-garden.jpg\" alt=\"Simple kitchen design for small house with vertical garden \" class=\"wp-image-14622\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/15172302\/simple-kitchen-design-for-small-house-with-certicle-garden.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/15172302\/simple-kitchen-design-for-small-house-with-certicle-garden-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/15172302\/simple-kitchen-design-for-small-house-with-certicle-garden-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/15172302\/simple-kitchen-design-for-small-house-with-certicle-garden-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A simple kitchen design with a mosaic LED-lit backsplash and top and bottom storage cabinets<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Bohemian Kitchen Interior Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This one wall kitchen interior design for a small house is for those who like blue and love a good bohemian backsplash. This kitchen has overhead with push-to-open cabinets with a combination of frosty glass and blue laminate for easy storage of crockery. Handleless bottom cabinets and drawers are also a part of this kitchen design. This kitchen has a frosty white marble countertop that is elegant in its design.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/15172229\/bohemian-kitchen-design-for-small-space-house-.jpg\" alt=\"One wall small kitchen for small house in white and blue\" class=\"wp-image-14619\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/15172229\/bohemian-kitchen-design-for-small-space-house-.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/15172229\/bohemian-kitchen-design-for-small-space-house--300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/15172229\/bohemian-kitchen-design-for-small-space-house--768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/15172229\/bohemian-kitchen-design-for-small-space-house--150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A kitchen with a bohemian backsplash and a seamless frosty white marble countertop<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Space saving kitchen designs that offer 20% extra space!\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/06165035\/space-saving-kitchen-designs-that-offer-20-extra-space-scaled.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Fun Themed Kitchen For A Small House<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you have a fun and peppy personality then this is the kitchen for you. This small kitchen in a bumblebee colour is a perfect little kitchen for a small house. This L-shaped kitchen has overhead cabinets with glass shutters in white and a medium-sized window with a ledge big enough to accommodate indoor plants. This small kitchen also has bottom cabinets and drawers. There is beige colour textured backsplash with hooks for easy hanging of spoons. A black granite countertop in an L shape is a part of this small kitchen layout.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/15172240\/l-shaped-kitchen-style-for-small-house.jpg\" alt=\"L-shaped white kitchen design for small space house\" class=\"wp-image-14620\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/15172240\/l-shaped-kitchen-style-for-small-house.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/15172240\/l-shaped-kitchen-style-for-small-house-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/15172240\/l-shaped-kitchen-style-for-small-house-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/15172240\/l-shaped-kitchen-style-for-small-house-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A kitchen in a unique colour palette of black, yellow and white with a brown textured backsplash<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Sophisticated Kitchen Setup<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This kitchen set up for a small house is simple and sophisticated in its looks. This kitchen has overhead cabinets and open shelves for easy storage of jars and other crockery. This kitchen also has bottom cabinets with pull to open mechanism and drawers to put away cutlery. The backsplash in this kitchen will remind you of the sea with its blue mosaics tiles. This kitchen has a dignified white granite countertop where cooking is made easy.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/15172317\/sophisticated-kitchen-setup-for-small-house-.jpg\" alt=\"Kitchen setup for small house with blue mosaics backsplash and open shelves\" class=\"wp-image-14623\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/15172317\/sophisticated-kitchen-setup-for-small-house-.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/15172317\/sophisticated-kitchen-setup-for-small-house--300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/15172317\/sophisticated-kitchen-setup-for-small-house--768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/15172317\/sophisticated-kitchen-setup-for-small-house--150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A sophisticated kitchen design with an airforce blue backsplash and hooks to hang spoons<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Parallel Kitchen Style<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This kitchen style for a small house is pretty much all you need if you have space constraints. This kitchen has a backsplash made from yellow and brown mosaic tiles. The kitchen has push to open overhead and bottom cabinets in white high gloss laminate. Parallel to the granite countertop in black is a tall unit with inbuilt oven storage. This kitchen design has corner shelves at the top to safely and securely store away your jars.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/15172253\/parallel-small-kitchen-for-small-house-.jpg\" alt=\"Parallel kitchen style for small house with mosaic backsplash\" class=\"wp-image-14621\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/15172253\/parallel-small-kitchen-for-small-house-.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/15172253\/parallel-small-kitchen-for-small-house--300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/15172253\/parallel-small-kitchen-for-small-house--768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/15172253\/parallel-small-kitchen-for-small-house--150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A kitchen with a neat black granite countertop and corner shelf storage option<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This what we at <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\">DesignCafe<\/a> reckon are some brilliant simple kitchen designs for a small house. We hope you enjoyed this read. Let us know what you think! Send us an email. Can&#8217;t wait to hear from you!\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Explore, More About<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/parallel-kitchen-designs-home\/\">Parallel Kitchen Designs<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/space-saving-ideas-for-small-kitchen\/\">Space-Saving Ideas For Small Kitchens<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/kitchen-backsplash-ideas\/\">Kitchen Backsplash Ideas<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Modular Kitchens At Best Prices<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Speak to our kitchen experts today!<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"labeltxt\">Enter your name*<\/span>  -->\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"form-row dc-falg-row\">\n        <!-- <div class=\"form-group col-md-3 guideForm\">\n            <select name=\"your-phone-ext\" id=\"id_select2_example\" class=\"id_select2_example drop-downfield form-dropdown\"\n                onfocus='this.size=5;' onblur='this.size=1;' onchange='this.size=1; this.blur();'\n                data-width=\"100%\" data-minimum-results-for-search=\"Infinity\">\n               \n                <option valu